{
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": {"type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --"},
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      },
      {
        "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_logs}"},
        "enable": true,
        "hide": false,
        "iconColor": "purple",
        "name": "Ollama model loads",
        "target": {
          "expr": "{host=\"wags-ai\", unit=\"ollama.service\"} |~ \"(?i)(load model|llm load progress|llama_model_load|new model load|starting runner|loaded runners)\"",
          "queryType": "range",
          "refId": "Annotations"
        },
        "textFormat": "Ollama load — {{__line__}}"
      },
      {
        "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_logs}"},
        "enable": true,
        "hide": false,
        "iconColor": "red",
        "name": "Ollama evictions",
        "target": {
          "expr": "{host=\"wags-ai\", unit=\"ollama.service\"} |~ \"(?i)(unload|stopped server|free memory|removing model)\"",
          "queryType": "range",
          "refId": "Annotations"
        },
        "textFormat": "Ollama eviction — {{__line__}}"
      }
    ]
  },
  "description": "Behind the demo — the bare-metal RTX 5090 box (wags-ai, 192.168.2.240) that serves every Ollama inference for ObserVIBElity. Captures VRAM thrash organically.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "links": [
    {
      "asDropdown": false,
      "icon": "external link",
      "includeVars": true,
      "keepTime": true,
      "tags": ["observibelity"],
      "title": "ObserVIBElity dashboards",
      "type": "dashboards"
    }
  ],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1000,
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "This is a **single Ubuntu box with one RTX 5090** (32 GB VRAM) running every Ollama model in the ObserVIBElity demo — *eleven* open-source LLMs (llama, qwen, mistral, gemma, phi, tinyllama) rotating through one GPU.\n\n**Story to watch:** the *VRAM by model* panel. When too many models load at once the stack collapses — Ollama evicts to make room and latency spikes downstream. Nothing staged.\n\n**Why this matters:** Sigil sees evaluations. The Vercel AI SDK sees app-side calls. *Neither* sees GPU temp, per-process VRAM, eviction churn, or Modelfile capability. **AI o11y is what justifies AI spend — use AI to diagnose AI.**"
      },
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "🤖 wags-ai right now — RTX 5090 + Ollama",
      "type": "row",
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 4},
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "GPU health — is this thing happy?",
      "description": "Green when VRAM<95%, ≥1 model loaded, no throttling, no ECC errors.",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 5, "x": 0, "y": 5},
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "textMode": "value",
        "justifyMode": "center"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {"type": "value", "options": {"1": {"text": "🟢 Healthy", "color": "#0F2A1A", "index": 0}, "0": {"text": "🔴 Investigate", "color": "#2A0F1A", "index": 1}}}
          ],
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"value": null, "color": "#F472B6"},
            {"value": 1, "color": "#86EFAC"}
          ]}
        }
      },
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A",
        "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
        "expr": "vector(scalar(max(nvidia_gpu_memory_used_bytes{host=\"wags-ai\"}) / max(nvidia_gpu_memory_total_bytes{host=\"wags-ai\"}) < bool 0.95) * scalar(max(ollama_loaded_models{host=\"wags-ai\"}) >= bool 1) * scalar(sum(nvidia_gpu_clock_event_reason_active{host=\"wags-ai\", reason!=\"gpu_idle\"}) == bool 0) * scalar((max(nvidia_gpu_ecc_errors_uncorrected_volatile_total{host=\"wags-ai\"}) == bool 0) or vector(1)))"
      }],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Stable for",
      "description": "Time since the last model eviction. A flat line on the loaded-count chart is the success story.",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 4, "x": 5, "y": 5},
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "textMode": "auto",
        "justifyMode": "center"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"value": null, "color": "#F472B6"},
            {"value": 300, "color": "#A78BFA"},
            {"value": 1800, "color": "#86EFAC"}
          ]},
          "unit": "s",
          "decimals": 0
        }
      },
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A",
        "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
        "expr": "(time() - max_over_time(timestamp(ollama_loaded_models{host=\"wags-ai\"} < (ollama_loaded_models{host=\"wags-ai\"} offset 30s))[6h:30s])) or vector(21600)"
      }],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Models loaded",
      "description": "How many models are resident in VRAM right now. Out of all those installed on disk.",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 4, "x": 9, "y": 5},
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "justifyMode": "center"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"value": null, "color": "#FB923C"},
            {"value": 1, "color": "#A78BFA"},
            {"value": 4, "color": "#86EFAC"}
          ]},
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {"refId": "A", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "max(ollama_loaded_models{host=\"wags-ai\"})", "legendFormat": "loaded"},
        {"refId": "B", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "max(ollama_installed_models{host=\"wags-ai\"})", "legendFormat": "installed"}
      ],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Electricity cost (range)",
      "description": "GPU power × current time range × $0.12/kWh. Drag the time picker; watch this update.",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 4, "x": 13, "y": 5},
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "textMode": "auto",
        "justifyMode": "center"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"value": null, "color": "#86EFAC"},
            {"value": 0.50, "color": "#A78BFA"},
            {"value": 5.00, "color": "#F472B6"}
          ]},
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 2
        }
      },
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A",
        "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
        "expr": "sum(avg_over_time(nvidia_gpu_power_draw_watts{host=\"wags-ai\", name=\"NVIDIA_GeForce_RTX_5090\"}[$__range])) * ($__range_s) / 3600 / 1000 * 0.12"
      }],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "GPU power",
      "description": "5090 ceiling is 575 W.",
      "type": "gauge",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 4, "x": 17, "y": 5},
      "options": {
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true,
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"value": null, "color": "#8AB8FF"},
            {"value": 200, "color": "#A78BFA"},
            {"value": 450, "color": "#F472B6"}
          ]},
          "unit": "watt",
          "min": 0, "max": 575, "decimals": 0
        }
      },
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A",
        "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
        "expr": "avg(nvidia_gpu_power_draw_watts{host=\"wags-ai\", name=\"NVIDIA_GeForce_RTX_5090\"})"
      }],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "GPU temp",
      "description": "Target <80°C, hardware throttles around 88°C.",
      "type": "gauge",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 3, "x": 21, "y": 5},
      "options": {
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true,
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"value": null, "color": "#8AB8FF"},
            {"value": 60, "color": "#A78BFA"},
            {"value": 80, "color": "#F472B6"}
          ]},
          "unit": "celsius",
          "min": 20, "max": 90, "decimals": 0
        }
      },
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A",
        "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
        "expr": "max(nvidia_gpu_temperature_gpu_celsius{host=\"wags-ai\"})"
      }],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "title": "💾 VRAM occupancy — watch this for eviction cycles",
      "type": "row",
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 10},
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "title": "VRAM by model (stacked) — collapse = eviction = the story",
      "description": "Each color is a model in VRAM. The 'other (driver + apps)' band accounts for non-Ollama use so the stack matches the hero VRAM-in-use total.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 11},
      "options": {
        "legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true, "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "min", "max"]},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 60,
            "gradientMode": "opacity",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "stacking": {"mode": "normal", "group": "A"},
            "spanNulls": true
          },
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "unit": "decbytes"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "other (driver + apps)"}, "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "#4B5563"}}]}
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {"refId": "A", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "ollama_loaded_model_size_vram_bytes{host=\"wags-ai\"}", "legendFormat": "{{model}}"},
        {"refId": "B", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "sum(nvidia_gpu_memory_used_bytes{host=\"wags-ai\"}) - sum(ollama_loaded_model_size_vram_bytes{host=\"wags-ai\"})", "legendFormat": "other (driver + apps)"}
      ],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "title": "Currently loaded models — the live roster competing for VRAM",
      "description": "Sorted by VRAM resident. Expires_in = seconds until idle-evict.",
      "type": "table",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 21},
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "sortBy": [{"displayName": "VRAM", "desc": true}]
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"custom": {"align": "auto"}},
        "overrides": [
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "VRAM"}, "properties": [{"id": "unit", "value": "decbytes"}]},
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Disk"}, "properties": [{"id": "unit", "value": "decbytes"}]},
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Expires"}, "properties": [{"id": "unit", "value": "s"}]}
        ]
      },
      "transformations": [
        {"id": "merge", "options": {}},
        {"id": "organize", "options": {
          "renameByName": {
            "model": "Model",
            "family": "Family",
            "parameter_size": "Size",
            "quantization": "Quant",
            "Value #VRAM": "VRAM",
            "Value #DISK": "Disk",
            "Value #EXP": "Expires"
          },
          "excludeByName": {"host": true, "cluster": true, "instance": true, "job": true, "Time": true, "digest": true, "__name__": true}
        }}
      ],
      "targets": [
        {"refId": "VRAM", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "ollama_loaded_model_size_vram_bytes{host=\"wags-ai\"} * on(model) group_left(family, parameter_size, quantization) ollama_loaded_model_info{host=\"wags-ai\"}", "format": "table", "instant": true},
        {"refId": "DISK", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "ollama_loaded_model_size_bytes{host=\"wags-ai\"}", "format": "table", "instant": true},
        {"refId": "EXP",  "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "ollama_loaded_model_expires_seconds{host=\"wags-ai\"}", "format": "table", "instant": true}
      ],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "title": "Loaded count over time — watch for the sawtooth of eviction",
      "description": "Flat = stable. Every dip is a real eviction event.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 21},
      "options": {
        "legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": false},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "single"}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 30,
            "gradientMode": "opacity",
            "lineInterpolation": "stepAfter",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "pointSize": 4,
            "spanNulls": true
          },
          "color": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "#A78BFA"},
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0
        }
      },
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "max(ollama_loaded_models{host=\"wags-ai\"})", "legendFormat": "loaded"}],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "title": "🌡️ GPU & demo workload",
      "type": "row",
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 31},
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "title": "GPU compute vs memory bus — saturation here is the real bottleneck",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 32},
      "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"}, "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 25, "gradientMode": "opacity", "lineInterpolation": "smooth", "lineWidth": 2, "showPoints": "never", "spanNulls": true},
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "unit": "percentunit", "min": 0, "max": 1
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {"refId": "A", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "avg(nvidia_gpu_utilization_gpu_ratio{host=\"wags-ai\"})", "legendFormat": "compute"},
        {"refId": "B", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "avg(nvidia_gpu_utilization_memory_ratio{host=\"wags-ai\"})", "legendFormat": "memory bus"}
      ],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "title": "Power & heat — is this thing screaming?",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 32},
      "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"}, "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 25, "gradientMode": "opacity", "lineInterpolation": "smooth", "lineWidth": 2, "showPoints": "never", "spanNulls": true},
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
        },
        "overrides": [
          {"matcher": {"id": "byFrameRefID", "options": "A"}, "properties": [{"id": "unit", "value": "watt"}, {"id": "custom.axisPlacement", "value": "left"}, {"id": "max", "value": 575}]},
          {"matcher": {"id": "byFrameRefID", "options": "B"}, "properties": [{"id": "unit", "value": "celsius"}, {"id": "custom.axisPlacement", "value": "right"}, {"id": "min", "value": 20}, {"id": "max", "value": 90}]}
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {"refId": "A", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "avg(nvidia_gpu_power_draw_watts{host=\"wags-ai\", name=\"NVIDIA_GeForce_RTX_5090\"})", "legendFormat": "power (W)"},
        {"refId": "B", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "max(nvidia_gpu_temperature_gpu_celsius{host=\"wags-ai\"})", "legendFormat": "temp (°C)"}
      ],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "title": "Demo traffic in — this is what's driving the GPU",
      "description": "Requests/sec hitting Ollama from the gateway. Spikes here should match the GPU compute panel.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 32},
      "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"}, "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 25, "gradientMode": "opacity", "lineInterpolation": "smooth", "lineWidth": 2, "showPoints": "never", "spanNulls": true},
          "color": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "#67E8F9"},
          "unit": "reqps"
        }
      },
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "sum(rate(gen_ai_client_operation_duration_seconds_count{service_namespace=\"observibelity\", gen_ai_system=\"ollama\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "ollama req/s (gateway)"}],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "title": "📜 Ollama activity log",
      "type": "row",
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 40},
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "title": "Ollama load/unload/error log — the receipts for every eviction",
      "type": "logs",
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_logs}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 41},
      "options": {
        "showTime": true, "showLabels": false, "showCommonLabels": false,
        "wrapLogMessage": true, "prettifyLogMessage": false, "enableLogDetails": true,
        "dedupStrategy": "none", "sortOrder": "Descending"
      },
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_logs}"}, "expr": "{host=\"wags-ai\", unit=\"ollama.service\"} |~ \"(?i)(load|unload|llm load progress|stopped server|llama_model|free memory|removing model|starting runner|loaded runners|error|panic)\""}],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "title": "🔧 Deep telemetry — troubleshoot any issue",
      "type": "row",
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 51},
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "title": "HTTP API request rate by endpoint",
      "description": "Real inference vs health-check chatter, split by path. Parsed from Ollama's own GIN access logs.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_logs}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 52},
      "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true, "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"]}, "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 25, "gradientMode": "opacity", "lineInterpolation": "smooth", "lineWidth": 1, "showPoints": "never", "stacking": {"mode": "normal", "group": "A"}},
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "unit": "reqps"
        }
      },
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_logs}"}, "expr": "sum by (path) (rate({host=\"wags-ai\", unit=\"ollama.service\"} |~ `\\[GIN\\]` | regexp `\\[GIN\\]\\s+\\S+\\s+-\\s+\\S+\\s+\\|\\s+(?P<status>\\d+)\\s+\\|\\s+(?P<duration>\\S+)\\s+\\|\\s+(?P<ip>\\S+)\\s+\\|\\s+(?P<method>\\w+)\\s+\"(?P<path>[^\"]+)\"` [$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "{{path}}"}],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "title": "HTTP API p95 latency by endpoint — Ollama's own clock",
      "description": "Server-side timing that Sigil/Vercel SDK can't see. P95 across each endpoint.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_logs}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 52},
      "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true, "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"]}, "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 25, "gradientMode": "opacity", "lineInterpolation": "smooth", "lineWidth": 1, "showPoints": "never"},
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "unit": "s"
        }
      },
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_logs}"}, "expr": "quantile_over_time(0.95, {host=\"wags-ai\", unit=\"ollama.service\"} |~ `\\[GIN\\]` | regexp `\\[GIN\\]\\s+\\S+\\s+-\\s+\\S+\\s+\\|\\s+(?P<status>\\d+)\\s+\\|\\s+(?P<duration>\\S+)\\s+\\|\\s+(?P<ip>\\S+)\\s+\\|\\s+(?P<method>\\w+)\\s+\"(?P<path>[^\"]+)\"` | unwrap duration(duration) [$__rate_interval]) by (path)", "legendFormat": "p95 {{path}}"}],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "title": "HTTP status codes — 5xx line should be at zero",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_logs}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 60},
      "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true, "calcs": ["sum", "lastNotNull"]}, "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {"drawStyle": "bars", "fillOpacity": 80, "gradientMode": "opacity", "lineWidth": 0, "showPoints": "never", "stacking": {"mode": "normal", "group": "A"}},
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {"matcher": {"id": "byRegexp", "options": "^5.*"}, "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "#F472B6"}}]},
          {"matcher": {"id": "byRegexp", "options": "^4.*"}, "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "#FB923C"}}]},
          {"matcher": {"id": "byRegexp", "options": "^2.*"}, "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "#8AB8FF"}}]}
        ]
      },
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_logs}"}, "expr": "sum by (status) (rate({host=\"wags-ai\", unit=\"ollama.service\"} |~ `\\[GIN\\]` | regexp `\\[GIN\\]\\s+\\S+\\s+-\\s+\\S+\\s+\\|\\s+(?P<status>\\d+)\\s+\\|\\s+(?P<duration>\\S+)\\s+\\|\\s+(?P<ip>\\S+)\\s+\\|\\s+(?P<method>\\w+)\\s+\"(?P<path>[^\"]+)\"` [$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "{{status}}"}],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "title": "GPU throttle status",
      "description": "Zero is good — nothing throttling. Anything above zero in 6h means the GPU was clock-limited.",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 60},
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "justifyMode": "center"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [{"type": "value", "options": {"0": {"text": "✓ No throttling", "color": "#86EFAC", "index": 0}}}],
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"value": null, "color": "#86EFAC"},
            {"value": 1, "color": "#FB923C"},
            {"value": 10, "color": "#F472B6"}
          ]},
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "sum(sum_over_time(nvidia_gpu_clock_event_reason_active{host=\"wags-ai\", reason!=\"gpu_idle\"}[6h]))", "legendFormat": "throttle samples (6h)"}],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "title": "Per-runner GPU memory — each ollama subprocess is one model fighting for space",
      "description": "Joined to model names via runner cmdline parsing.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 68},
      "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true, "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"]}, "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 50, "gradientMode": "opacity", "lineInterpolation": "smooth", "lineWidth": 1, "showPoints": "never", "stacking": {"mode": "normal", "group": "A"}},
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "unit": "decbytes"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {"refId": "A", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "sum by (model) (nvidia_gpu_process_used_memory_bytes{host=\"wags-ai\"} * on(pid) group_left(model) ollama_runner_info{host=\"wags-ai\"})", "legendFormat": "{{model}}"},
        {"refId": "B", "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"}, "expr": "sum by (process_name) (nvidia_gpu_process_used_memory_bytes{host=\"wags-ai\", process_name!~\"/usr/local/bin/ollama\"})", "legendFormat": "other: {{process_name}}"}
      ],
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "title": "Disk read throughput — the cost of a cold model load",
      "description": "Spikes = a model loaded from NVMe. An 8B Q4 cold-load = ~5 GB read in a few seconds.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 77},
